    <string name="help_search_hint">What are you looking for?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_title">Frequently Asked Questions</string>
    <string name="help_faq_q1">How to add an income or expense?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_a1">You can add a transaction by tapping the \"+\" button on the main screen → select Income/Expense → enter the amount and description → Save. The app will automatically categorize and display it on the Overview page.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_q2">Can I edit or delete a transaction?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_a2">Yes. Just tap on the transaction you want to manage → select \"Edit\" or \"Delete\". Note: deleted transactions cannot be recovered.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_q3">Does the app automatically calculate total income/expense by day, week, or month?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_a3">Yes. The Overview page automatically updates charts and summary figures for the time range you select. You can also filter by each spending category.</string>
    <string name="help_faq_q4">Can I back up or restore my data?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_a4">Yes. Go to Settings → Backup &amp; Restore, then choose:

- Back up to Google Drive
- Export as CSV file (advanced option)</string>
    <string name="help_faq_q5">How can I get quick support or ask the AI assistant?</string>
    <string name="help_faq_a5">If you want to explain a transaction, analyze your spending, or need a quick answer — use the AI Assistant by tapping the \"Ask AI Assistant\" button in the Help section or on the main screen.</string>
    <string name="help_ask_ai_button">Ask AI Assistant</string>
